Invite a member to the organization

Usage:
  agentclash org members invite <orgId> [flags]

Flags:
      --email string   Email address to invite (required)
  -h, --help           help for invite
      --role string    Role: org_admin, org_member (default "org_member")

Global Flags:
      --api-url string     API base URL (overrides config)
      --json               Output in JSON format
      --no-color           Disable color output
      --non-interactive    Disable interactive prompts (also honored: CI=true, AGENTCLASH_NON_INTERACTIVE=1, --json, no TTY)
  -o, --output string      Output format: table, json, yaml
  -q, --quiet              Suppress non-essential output
  -v, --verbose            Enable debug output on stderr
  -w, --workspace string   Workspace ID (overrides config)
      --yes                Skip confirmation prompts
